# Project Brain — Digitify Lead Search

Je werkt in **Digitify Lead Search** (`digitify-lead-search`), een pnpm monorepo voor lead generation, outbound e-mail, CRM, en marketing modules.

## Eerste stap bij elke taak

1. Lees [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) (repo root)
2. Raadpleeg [docs/PROJECT_BRAIN.md](../../docs/PROJECT_BRAIN.md) voor architectuur
3. Zoek feature in [docs/MODULE_MAP.md](../../docs/MODULE_MAP.md)
4. Check [docs/TODO.md](../../docs/TODO.md) en [docs/DECISIONS.md](../../docs/DECISIONS.md)

## Stack (kort)

- **App:** `apps/web` — Next.js 15, React 19, tRPC client
- **API:** `packages/api` — tRPC routers + `lib/` business logic
- **DB:** `packages/db` — Prisma + PostgreSQL + optional RLS
- **UI:** `@digitify/ui` — shared components

## Kritieke regels

### Tenant / workspace
- `workspaceId` = **owner user id** (`users.id`), niet `workspaces.id`
- Tenant-rijen: `createdById = workspaceId`
- Productie: `ENABLE_WORKSPACE_RLS=true` verplicht
- Zie `packages/api/src/lib/WORKSPACE.md`

### Code conventies
- Minimale diff; geen unrelated refactors
- Business logic in `packages/api/src/lib/`, niet alleen in pages
- UI copy in **Nederlands**
- Match bestaande imports, naming, patterns in nabije code
- **Commit niet** tenzij user expliciet vraagt

### E-mail
- Nooit auto-send: draft → approval → send

### Waar code staat
| Taak | Pad |
|------|-----|
| tRPC endpoint | `packages/api/src/routers/{feature}.router.ts` → `root.ts` |
| UI page | `apps/web/src/app/(app)/{feature}/` |
| Component | `apps/web/src/components/{feature}/` |
| DB model | `packages/db/prisma/schema.prisma` |
| Cron | `apps/web/src/app/api/cron/` |
| Public API | `apps/web/src/app/api/public/` |
| Nav/modules | `apps/web/src/lib/navigation.ts`, `module-access.ts` |

## Tests vóór afronden

```bash
pnpm test
pnpm typecheck
# Bij DB/RLS: RUN_DB_INTEGRATION=1 ENABLE_WORKSPACE_RLS=true pnpm test:integration
```

